import React from "react";
import { VStack, Button } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import FeatureIcon from "../featureIcons";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
const SpeakerFeaturedMenu = () => {
  return (
    <VStack spacing={10} align="center">
      <FeatureIcon
        alt="thumbometer"
        src="/thumb.png"
        link="/thumb"
        heading="Thumb-o-meter"
        subheading="Hows it going?"
      />
      <FeatureIcon
        alt="raisehand"
        src="/raisehand.jpeg"
        link="/raisehand"
        heading="Raise a Hand"
        subheading="Got a question?"
      />
      <FeatureIcon
        alt="livequiz"
        src="/quizzical.jpeg"
        link="/quiz"
        heading="Live Quiz"
        subheading="How much do you understand?"
      />
      <FeatureIcon
        alt="djDeck"
        src="/quizzical.jpeg"
        link="/deck"
        heading="DJ Deck"
        subheading="A little bit of music you say?"
      />
      <Button>
        <Link to="/admin">Admin</Link>
      </Button>
    </VStack>
  );
};

export default SpeakerFeaturedMenu;
